Class ConferenceTest

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_proceedings.model.conference.ConferenceTest
public class ConferenceTest extends Object
Unit tests for the Conference class. Tests adding, editing, and removing sessions and accepted items, assigning items to sessions, and saving to a file.
